snippet.textDisplay: Ok here’s my thing. This is NOT an attack but simply a stating of facts. You seemingly communicated with the spirit you were looking to communicate with. The second it tries, you turn back. Personally, I do not use the ouija board because it is so negative. However, if you’re going to start a conversation and start getting responses but decide to close out, why even do it in the first place? All you’re doing is frustrating the spirit. Do you understand the energy it takes for them to communicate like that? Think of it like a conversation with someone you know. You’re trying to talk to them, trying to get them to ENGAGE with you, but the second they open their mouth, you turn around and run away. How do you think the other end of the conversation is going to feel? They’re going to be frustrated and will either try to get your attention back or simply lash out in anger. Spirits have all the same feelings we do. If you continue to treat them disrespectfully by not trying to listen and understand what they’re saying, I can guarantee you’re going to continue to have events like this happen. I agree do not try the board again. But you need to understand why it is that this being has continuously appeared in your life for so very long. Otherwise, you will only stress yourself out further and that will impact your physical, mental, spiritual, and emotional health. Also, as a practiced individual with smudging, you MUST SURROUND YOURSELF WITH THE SAGE!!!! Don’t just wave it in front of y’all. You have to completely circle your entire body making sure to reach every inch possible. That little wave up and down and side-to-side y’all keep doing is doing you as much good as not doing it at all because you are leaving 99.9% of your body exposed to attachment. I am a witch of Wicca and I have been practicing smudging myself like this for almost seven years now and have yet to get an attachment. Also, each of you needs hematite in some form. Preferably rings but stones or necklaces or bracelets will work as well. Hematite collects all of the negative energy impacting and inside of you and will break when it has reached its capacity and is done. When this happens, get some more. Also, if you hold a piece of clear quartz in your right hand, it will also suck up all of the negative energy within you, though it will likely not break like the hematites can. While holding the quartz in your RIGHT hand, have a piece of ROSE quartz in your LEFT hand as this will fill you with positivity, light, and love. The way to remember this is RIGHT hand = RELEASE and LEFT hand = LET IN. You want to release the negativity and let in the positivity. Do this while meditating. That’s what my reiki master taught me and it helps me let go of stress, anxiety, everything. A wonderful meditation y’all should try out: Start out by sitting/standing with your feet completely flat to the ground. Clear your mind. Imagine you are surrounded by a ball of white light. Above you is a swirling purple cloud. This is the Universe, the collection of all POSITIVE energy. Below you is the Earth and it is red as it is the collection of all NEGATIVE energy. As you are breathing deeply and slowly, purple tendrils from the Universe gently come down through your crown and spread through you like your veins as they travel down your body. As they reach your feet, they start changing from purple to red. These now red tendrils will go down to the core of the Earth and, when they have connected with it’s very center, you will now be grounded. Now, as you are grounded, with your third eye focus back on your ball of white light. As you are looking out from your protective field, mirrors come to cover your ball. Their backs are towards you with the reflective side out. Not a single centimeter or sliver of your white light can come out as the final mirror is placed. Now, all negativity that should wish to befall you will bounce back to wherever it came from. NOTHING and NO ONE can get into your ball and influence your energy without YOUR PERMISSION. This is a REALLY good meditation to start your day with and should help to give a sense of security on adventures with spirit. I know most will probably not stick around to read all of this but, for those of you that have, try this meditation out and see how it works for you in your life!!

See my story. For:cory. If you do see this and find it interesting tell my story please. From: tiffany capehart

I have several. Not really scary or bad but creepy and weird..... Here we go.

1st story: when I was little I had these two dolls. (I got told this by my mother) it was a boy and a girl. Their names were Richard and the little girls name I do not know. When I was all alone I had conversations with them and I would laugh and talk all day with them. They would come out when my mom or dad wasn't around. They would actually come out as real 'people like you or me. My mom came out one day and saw them and I guess they just disappeared. I don't really remember or see them anymore.

2nd story: it's a short one. At this time of the story I was about like 10 months of so. My mom had just put me down for bed and bout an hour later she heard my laughing (it was pitch black btw) and I somehow got OUT of my crib, even tho I couldn't walk or anything, and got all the way across the room in front of my closet and sat in front of it and started laughing and I was just looking at the closet PITCH black. So if course my mom wanted to see why I was laughing so she got out of bed and went to open my door.. She reached for the Handel and pulled.. It wouldn't open so she keep pulling and pushing and pushing and pulling till it finaly opened. she grabbed me and ran.

3rd story is about everyday of my life now: not to bad but still scary af: so everyday when I walk to the bus stop for school I see the REALLY tall man thing (I dunno if it's a boy or girl) and when I walk to the bus stop I look behind me cuz I'm always paranoid at 6 in the morning lol. And I see him/her look out of behind a tree and just watch me walk to the stop. He/shes pitch black. All i can see is it's shoulder and head. I call him/her the shadow man. I forgot about your Ghost dude that follows you so I just wanted to share this cuz I remember you call ur demon thing the shadow man

Thanks for taking your time and reading this (if you even do cuz I know it's a LOT to read.)
I love y'alls channel. You guys are my favourite youtubers!!!!!
Lots of love, tiffany C.
